<paragraph id="IFRS15_C2"><paranum>C2</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 15"/><data name="paranum" value="C2"/></prolog><body><variant base="F49527410" id="IFRS15_C2_V2">       <p id="IFRS15_P0827">For the purposes of the transition requirements in <xref base="F51966476" href="IFRS15_C3.dita#IFRS15_C3" id="IFRS15_X0815">paragraphs C3&#x2013;C8A</xref>:</p>       <ol base="F49527411" id="IFRS15_L0091" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value>           <p base="F49527413" id="IFRS15_P0828">the date of initial application is the start of the reporting period in which an entity first applies this Standard; and</p>         </li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value>           <p base="F49527415" id="IFRS15_P0829">a completed contract is a <xref base="SL31717224" href="IFRS15_APPA.dita#IFRS15_APPA/IFRS15_P0498">contract<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0049"/></ph></xref> for which the entity has transferred all of the goods or services identified in accordance with <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_number">IAS 11</ph> <ph outputclass="standard_title">Construction Contracts</ph></ph>, <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_number">IAS 18</ph> <ph outputclass="standard_title">Revenue</ph></ph> and related Interpretations.                        </p>         </li></ol>     </variant></body></paragraph>